{"tid":700441,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"下季皇馬仲會唔會得到足總既眷顧？","createTime":"2018-06-13T10:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T11:02:51.000Z","uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"01b38f718c48476ce6ca21bfc27d2b0de8529913","tid":700441,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T10:45:34.000Z","msg":"咁樣撚西班牙足總<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce80cdc8d415ad25841eee94ea0735fa30e35ea","tid":700441,"uid":35176,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T10:48:39.000Z","msg":"西班牙足協主席盧比亞賴斯在發布會上宣布了盧柏迪古離任的消息，他也談到了做出這個決定的原因。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;西班牙足協不能允許足協工作人員私底下有談判，而且在<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>公告5分鐘前我們才知道</strong></span>，我們只好這麼做了。如果有人想和我們的工作人員建立關係，那他得和足協談判。國家隊是最為重要的，世界杯是最重要的賽事。&ldquo;<br />\n&ldquo;我很欣賞盧柏迪古，也很尊重他，我認為他是一位頂級教練，這讓我做這個決定尤為艱難。&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;國家隊是所有西班牙人的，他們不能這麼做事，在世界杯前的2-3天。我們必須做出這個決定。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"7063c26932e1096b1132b3863cae84159e5c5978","tid":700441,"uid":130419,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T10:50:24.000Z","msg":"足總又點 西甲主席是皇馬球迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2228ab6999db47c300ca810e4c50d525ef125240","tid":700441,"uid":25345,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T10:51:54.000Z","msg":"有撚照顧咩<br />\n疤兩年冇輸12碼<br />\nbig gay無限手球都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18eb3a3ff52e3190e4255befcd5797287affb553","tid":700441,"uid":35176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2228ab6999db47c300ca810e4c50d525ef125240","tid":700441,"uid":25345,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T10:51:54.000Z","msg":"有撚照顧咩<br />\n疤兩年冇輸12碼<br />\nbig gay無限手球都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hah